component.description: The component used for the root node. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.

disableColorScheme.description: Disable color-scheme CSS property. For more details, check out https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color-scheme For browser support, check out https://caniuse.com/?search=color-scheme
